<paragraph pageId="633" pageNumber="634">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="633" pageNumber="634">
This species ranges from southwestern British Columbia, including Vancouver Island (Lindroth 1969a: 962), south to southern California (Ball 1959: 200-201). One old specimen labeled 
<normalizedToken originalValue="“Nev.”">&quot;Nev.&quot;</normalizedToken>
is known (Ball 1959: 200).
</paragraph>
